	⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⣾⠈⢧⠀⠀⠀⢡⠀⠹⣄⠀⢧⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠸⠀⢠⡎⠀⡜⠀⠀⠀⡰⠁⣧⠏⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n\
	⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠀⠈⢣⡀⠀⠀⢇⠀⢻⣦⣸⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣇⡰⡿⠀⠰⠁⠀⢀⡜⠁⠀⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n\
	⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠱⡄⠀⠸⡄⠈⡆⠙⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⠛⢡⠁⢀⠇⠀⢠⠞⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n\
